TestTool.Model.TestGrading

Class TestScore

  • java.lang.Object
    • TestTool.Model.TestCreation.Test
      • TestTool.Model.TestGrading.TestScore

  • public abstract class TestScore
extends Test
    TestScore holds the overall score and progress of scoring for a test. A TestScore is associated with a Test, which holds all of the Questions to be scored. This class also holds a collection of QuestionScores.
